commit.message: Add ProbabilityMeasure type.
Add non-greedy Cart prod operator.
Add set subset operators.
Fix distinct bug in Set.
Relation class uses PredicateExpr.
Add Relation class.
Set enumerator should use distinct values. Added Relation interfaces.
Add Field class. Add Probability and RealAnalysis projects.
SetAlgebra uses min and max of subsets ordered by |<|. SigmaAlgebra checks the parent and empty set are present as distinguished members.
Add SubSets type. SetAlgebra implements ITotalOrder and IEnumerble. Add SigmaAlgebra type.
Correct order of greatest/leasr parameters for Lattice.
Add SetAlgebra. Lattices have correct parameters.
Add Kinds project. Algebraic structures have correct number of ops. Add BooleanAlgebra types.
Add BoundedLattice definition.
Correct order op implementation.
Remove order parameter from SemiLattice as join induces order.
Remove Subsets n method as it is not implemented correctly.
FiniteSet implements IEnumerable. Subsets method takes parameter for max length of subset. Add Powerset property.
Ordered structures use correct IEnumerable implementation. Integer ring stuctures use own IEnumerable implementation.
Add ring N.
Z rings use object expressions.
Add Order, Identity, Inverse interfaces.
Implement Cartesian product operator. infiniteSeq takes predicate first.
Lattice implements IPartialOrder.
Add set-element complement operator.
Test for Seq and SetGenerator in union and intersection set operators.
SetGenerator uses actual seq for parameter. infiniteSeq uses SetGenerator.
Add Complement method. Don't check for set finiteness by default.
Update README.
Fix README formatting.
